data.description: Welcome to this 3 bedroom and 2 and half bath home with a very large bonus room! Enjoy entertaining family and friends this upcoming holiday season in your new home! The oversized great room that leads into the dining room and kitchen is perfect for large gatherings! The private fenced in backyard boasts a firepit that is ideal for these cool nights! You will also enjoy extra storage in the garage and the outdoor storage shed!
